      • matchesThisPacket

        public boolean matchesThisPacket(org.projectfloodlight.openflow.types.DatapathId switchDpid,
                                 org.projectfloodlight.openflow.types.OFPort inPort,
                                 Ethernet packet,
                                 AllowDropPair adp)
        Checks if this rule is a match for the incoming packet's MatchFields
        参数:
        switchDpid - the Id of the connected switch
        inPort - the switch port where the packet originated from
        packet - the Ethernet packet that arrives at the switch
        allow-drop-pair - the pair of matches (allow and drop) given by the Firewall module that is used by the Firewall module's matchWithRule method to derive the match object for the decision to be taken
        返回:
        true if the rule matches the given packet-in, false otherwise
